beer.beer_description:
In celebration of a bumper hay season after years of drought we brew this HAYZY!
Brewed with barley, wheat, oats, chit malt, lactose & silage - Pasture grasses fermented anaerobically with naturally occurring lactic acid bacteria.
Hopped with Bru 1, Sabro & Galaxy.
